• Contains sidecar proxy, service discover, laod balancing and circuit breaker.
  • In general, it is an infrastructure that enables microservices to communicate with each other.

These proxies are not just for communication; We can also use it for requirements such as load balancing, authorization (authentication/authorization), encryption (encryption), monitoring and circuit breaker in case of error.
